      <title>沃尔沃因软件故障召回所有全电动 EX30 汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/volvo-recalls-all-fully-electric-ex30-cars-on-software-glitch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于软件问题，沃尔沃汽车公司宣布召回其新旗舰车型——全电动 EX30，共计近 72,000 辆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/volvo-recalls-all-fully-electric-ex30-cars-on-software-glitch</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 09:32:52 GMT</pubDate>
